@Skinah I'm sorry but it's not possible to do it in a safe way.
The addon doesn't use commons code at all, but the influxdb driver uses it and it's not documented as an optional dependency.
Also, I don't know if it applied to that dependency because up to my knowledge  there isn't any support for csv parsing in Java 11
